The '''''Devonian''''' was an [[Assault shuttle/Legends|assault shuttle]] used in the [[First Battle of Borleias]]. [[Judder Page/Legends|Judder Page]] was on the ship, which was saved from [[TIE/IN interceptor/Legends|TIE interceptors]] by [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]] under [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]].

It was also part of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] fleet during the [[Liberation of Coruscant (Galactic Civil War)|Liberation of Coruscant]]. Along with the [[Ryloth (CR90 corvette)|''Ryloth'']], the ship was dispatched by [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Gial Ackbar/Legends|Ackbar]] to rescue any survivors on a crippled [[Golan III Space Defense NovaGun|Golan III]].

